rows.label: qst200713_msg0001
rows.name:
Th-thanks, you saved me.
I'm so happy to be alive...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0002
rows.name:
Honestly...
If we hadn't come around, you'd
have been Igna kibble by now.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0003
rows.name:
And I'm grateful that you did!
Thank you again.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0004
rows.name:
But however though!
The game is still afoot!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0005
rows.name:
You think just because you saved
Yumyum's life, he'll roll over and
let you win? As if!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0006
rows.name:
You wanna keep going?
I thought you'd have learned by now...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0007
rows.name: Unquestionably!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0020
rows.name:
...Having said that, there's a lot of
frisky Ignas around here. That's tough.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0008
rows.name:
Perhaps if I could propose a truce,
we could cooperate for the time being,
for the safety and wellbeing of all?

rows.label: qst200713_msg0009
rows.name:
Because you're scared,
is what I'm getting.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0010
rows.name: N-n-n-n-no! Not me! Never!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0011
rows.name: ...Whatever you say, skipper.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0012
rows.name:
It's not me who's got fur in the game,
so how 'bout we let Idaten decide.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0013
rows.name: Oh oho ho...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0014
rows.name: Tora not sure Idaten listening. Again...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0015
rows.name: Ha?!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0016
rows.name: What was that?

rows.label: qst200713_msg0017
rows.name:
The fungal smell is getting stronger.
The Bloomshroom must be close!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0018
rows.name:
You heard him.
Keep up, or we're leaving you behind.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0019
rows.name: Y-y-yes ma'am!
